{"tid":1971861,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"(香港足球專輯)永遠的6號天才球員 - 蔡賀龍，一路好走","createTime":"2020-04-14T07:50:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-19T18:38:01.000Z","uid":73381,"like":24,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"2e9f0733fdaa17f10e090cb632f9f2dbfe2896ed","tid":1971861,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T07:50:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/_znnGcwYYs8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F_znnGcwYYs8&d=lExWnqkLii2%2BVYlrfbo%2B81UwqJDRuBhX9JYyxoGH6Hk%3D&h=4ddfa9b0\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/_znnGcwYYs8</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n直至昨晚8時許，阿龍曾用WhatsApp向他查問傷勢，「佢問老豆你而家點呀？我仲答佢都係咁啦，腰骨都係有啲痛，聽日可能出到院」，更明言明天會去接他出院，豈料至晚上10時左右便收到噩耗。<br />\n<br />\n他指阿龍自小喜歡踢波，獲獎無數，又曾揚言希望自己有朝一日成為足球先生，現時他只能望着阿龍早年得到的獎杯，睹物思人，「點解要走咗去？點解要留低我一個人孤零零」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20200409/DEPSFF6XLTNFVDZ5QA2TDTXJNE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20200409%2FDEPSFF6XLTNFVDZ5QA2TDTXJNE%2F&d=lExWnqkLii2%2BVYlrfbo%2B81UwqJDRuBhX9JYyxoGH6Hk%3D&h=fcc29cca\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20200409%2FDEPSFF6XLTNFVDZ5QA2TDTXJNE%2F&h=63cc59af\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20200409/DEPSFF6XLTNFVDZ5QA2TDTXJNE/</a><br />\n<br />\nR.I.P <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"125e6621cbb345f60bb21cf0200eae38238fee32","tid":1971861,"uid":199392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T08:08:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c62e7abd098a6106da9e83b0deff47b433163237","tid":1971861,"uid":26380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T08:33:14.000Z","msg":"RIP"},{"pid":"8e3e96546b4b38d6